{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 70,
    "name": "سُورَةُ المَعَارِجِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Ma'aarij",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Ascending Stairways",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 44,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5376,
        "text": "有人曾请求一种将发生的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5377,
        "text": "那是为不信的人们而预定的，没有任何人能加以抵抗。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5378,
        "text": "那是真主--天梯的主宰--发出的，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5379,
        "text": "众天神和精神在一日之内升到他那里。那一日的长度是五万年。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5380,
        "text": "你安然地忍受吧。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5381,
        "text": "他们以为那刑罚是很远的，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5382,
        "text": "我却以为那是很近的。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5383,
        "text": "在那日天像熔铜，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5384,
        "text": "山像彩绒。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5385,
        "text": "亲戚相见不相问。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5386,
        "text": "罪人愿意赎取那日的刑罚，即使牺牲他的儿女、",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5387,
        "text": "他的妻子、他的弟兄，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5388,
        "text": "和那收容他的血族，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5389,
        "text": "以及大地上所有的人，但愿那能拯救自己。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5390,
        "text": "绝不然，那确是发焰的烈火，",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5391,
        "text": "能揭去头皮，",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5392,
        "text": "能召唤转身而逃避的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5393,
        "text": "他曾聚积财产而加以保藏，",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5394,
        "text": "人确是被造成浮躁的，",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5395,
        "text": "遭遇灾殃的时候是烦恼的，",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5396,
        "text": "获得财富的时候是吝啬的。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5397,
        "text": "只有礼拜的人们，不是那样，",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5398,
        "text": "他们是常守拜功的；",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5399,
        "text": "他们的财产中有一个定份，",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5400,
        "text": "是用於施济乞丐和贫民的；",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5401,
        "text": "他们是承认报应之日的；",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5402,
        "text": "他们是畏惧他们的主的刑罚的。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5403,
        "text": "他们的主的刑罚，确是难保不降临的。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5404,
        "text": "他们是保守贞操的，",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5405,
        "text": "除非对自己的妻子和奴婢，他们确是不因此而受责备的；",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5406,
        "text": "凡在这个范围之外有所要求的人，都是过份的。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5407,
        "text": "他们是尊重自己所受的信托，和自己所缔的盟约的；",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5408,
        "text": "他们是秉公作证的；",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5409,
        "text": "他们是谨守拜功的。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5410,
        "text": "这等人，是在乐园中受优待的。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 502,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5411,
        "text": "不信道的人们，怎么注视著你，三五成群的分列",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5412,
        "text": "在你的左右呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5413,
        "text": "难道他们每个人都希望入恩泽的乐园吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5414,
        "text": "绝不然！我确已用他们所知道的物质创造了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 569,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5415,
        "text": "不然，我以一切东方和西方的主盟誓，我确是全能的，",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5416,
        "text": "我能以比他们更好的人代替他们，我不是无能的。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5417,
        "text": "你应当任他们妄谈，任他们游戏，直到他们看到他们所被警告的日子。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5418,
        "text": "在那日，他们将从坟中出来奔走，他们好像奔到牌位一样，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5419,
        "text": "同时，他们身遭凌辱，不敢仰视。那是他们被警告的日子。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 570,
        "ruku": 503,
        "hizbQuarter": 228,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
